quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  85,1,"By the sky containing great stars"
  85,2,"And [by] the promised Day"
  85,3,"And [by] the witness and what is witnessed,"
  85,4,"Destroyed [i.e., cursed] were the companions of the trench<sup foot_note=197740>1</sup>",footnotes:197740:1
  85,5,"[Containing] the fire full of fuel,"
  85,6,"When they were sitting near it."
  85,7,"And they, to what they were doing against the believers, were witnesses. <sup foot_note=197741>1</sup>",footnotes:197741:1
  85,8,"And they resented them not except because they believed in Allāh, the Exalted in Might, the Praiseworthy,"
  85,9,"To whom belongs the dominion of the heavens and the earth. And Allāh, over all things, is Witness.<sup foot_note=197742>1</sup>",footnotes:197742:1
  85,10,"Indeed, those who have tortured<sup foot_note=197743>1</sup> the believing men and believing women and then have not repented will have the punishment of Hell, and they will have the punishment of the Burning Fire.",footnotes:197743:1